    <h1>Welcome to Message API</h1>

    <p>Endpoints:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><code>POST /messages</code>: Creates a new message</li>
        <li><code>GET /messages</code>: Returns all messages</li>
        <li><code>GET /messages/summary</code>: Returns the total number of messages and the average message length</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To create a new message, send a POST request to <code>/messages</code> with the message content in the request body.</p>

